limit.test.js\",\"[2026-04-07] [REVIEWED by alice] Fresh verification complete per C15/C16: bob/tests/integration/kalshi_client_rate_limit.test.js passed 3/3 on 2026-04-07; KalshiClient /v1 path fix and rate-limit coverage verified. \u2014 deliverable: agents/bob/output/\"]}", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
