{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_3", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'source ../../scripts/agent_tools.sh && read_inbox'", "aggregated_output": "[agent_tools] Loaded for tina. Available: task_claim, task_done, task_inreview, task_review, task_progress, task_list, my_tasks, create_task, post, announce, dm, broadcast, read_inbox, read_peer, read_knowledge, read_culture, pipeline_status, log_progress\n--- 2026_04_03_22_04_01_from_ceo.processed.md ---\n## Sprint Kickoff \u2014 D004 Pipeline Push\n\n**Priority:** Get the trading pipeline running end-to-end.\n\n### What's ready:\n\n--- 2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.processed.md ---\n## Sprint 2 Kickoff \u2014 Signal Generation & Backtesting\n\nSprint 1 COMPLETE: 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\n\n### Sprint 2 Focus:\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_09_36_from_bob.processed.md ---\nT555 ready for review. Signal generator complete \u2014 z-score mean reversion strategy on correlated pairs. 18 signals generated, 8 paper trades simulated. Deliverables in output/: signal_generator.js, trade_signals.json, paper_trade_results.json. Run: cd agents/bob/output && node run_pipeline.js --with-signals\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_14_39_from_bob.processed.md ---\nT567 backtest ready for review. Walk-forward backtest of z-score strategy on 100-tick price histories. 4 trades, all stop-losses \u2014 confirms synthetic data limitation, real Kalshi data needed. Deliverable: output/backtest_signals.js + output/backtest_report.json. Run: node backtest_signals.js\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_22_58_from_bob.processed.md ---\nT568 parameter sweep ready for review. 64 z-score threshold combos tested via walk-forward backtest. Best: z_entry=1.0, z_exit=0.3, z_stop=4.0. Deliverable: output/parameter_sweep.js + output/parameter_sweep_results.json. Run: node parameter_sweep.js\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_39_44_from_ceo.processed.md ---\nSprint 3. Task T570: QA the backtest results from Dave.\n\nWAIT for Dave's backtest_results.json. Validate signal count, P&L math, drawdown tracking, no data leakage.\nOutput qa_backtest_report.md. DM olivia for final review. Post results to team_channel.\n\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_41_57_from_dave.processed.md ---\nT568 backtest complete \u2014 18 trades, 61.1% win rate, +$14.26 P&L (14.14% return), Sharpe 9.90, max DD 1.92%. Output: dave/output/backtest_results.json. Ready for your review.\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_44_43_from_olivia.processed.md ---\n# T570 \u2014 QA Needed Urgently\n\n**From:** Olivia (Quality Gate)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_45_54_from_alice.processed.md ---\n# T570 \u2014 START QA NOW\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n**Priority:** HIGH\n\n--- 2026_04_04_00_51_41_from_olivia.processed.md ---\n# T570 APPROVED \u2014 Excellent QA Work\n\n**From:** Olivia (Quality Gate)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\n\n--- 2026_04_04_02_34_06_from_dave.processed.md ---\nT568 REWORKED \u2014 all 5 fixes applied: spread-based P&L, Bob's actual 47 signals, pair dedup, z-score validation, 70/30 split. Results: 22.7% win, -$1.33 P&L, Sharpe -9.33 \u2014 matches your QA reference. Output: dave/output/backtest_results.json. Ready for re-validation.\n\n--- 2026_04_04_03_03_05_from_system.processed.md ---\nT577 APPROVED. Ran the test myself \u2014 38/38 PASS confirmed. Excellent regression suite covering the full Sprint 3 chain. This is exactly the kind of automated quality gate we need.\n\n--- 2026_04_04_12_32_13_from_olivia.processed.md ---\nT583 APPROVED \u2014 41/41 PASS. Excellent E2E coverage with Cholesky-correlated mock data. Pipeline trace verified end-to-end. Great work Tina. \u2014 Olivia\n\n--- 2026_04_04_13_23_48_from_alice.processed.md ---\n# Review Request: T581 \u2014 Pipeline Monitoring Dashboard\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\n\n--- 2026_04_04_13_29_48_from_alice.processed.md ---\n# Review Request: T580 \u2014 Walk-Forward Validation\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\n\n--- 2026_04_04_13_40_34_from_bob.processed.md ---\nT587 capital floor ready for QA. capital_floor.js (22/22 tests pass) + walk_forward_backtest_v2.js with $50 floor. Run: node output/capital_floor.js (unit tests), node output/walk_forward_backtest_v2.js (integration). Capital floor correctly catches negative capital and halts trading.\n\n--- 2026_04_04_14_23_43_from_bob.processed.md ---\n# T588 Ready for QA \u2014 Rate Limit Integration Test\n\n20/20 tests pass. Run: `cd agents/bob/output && node rate_limit_integration_test.js`\nTests burst requests, backoff timing, concurrent access, window reset, and CredentialManager integration.\n\n--- 2026_04_06_12_14_48_from_ceo.processed.md ---\n# Sprint 4 \u2014 From Founder\n\nTina \u2014 you have T583 (QA review).\nWait for DM from Dave confirming pipeline_report.md is ready.\nReview all pipeline outputs, write output/sprint4_qa_report.md\n\n--- 2026_04_06_23_23_42_from_alice_sprint4_t583.processed.md ---\n# Sprint 4 Assignment \u2014 T583\n\nTina,\n\nFollowing D7 and C13, your Sprint 4 task is T583.\n\n--- 2026_04_06_23_30_00_from_alice_sprint4_task583.processed.md ---\n# Sprint 4 assignment \u2014 T583\n\nWait for Dave's DM before starting.\n\nThen:\n\n", "exit_code": 1, "status": "failed"}}
