 focus: risk management and system hardening.** P1 tasks: per-trade stop-loss (T714/Dave), capital floor (T715/Bob), rate limit testing (T716/Bob), velocity tracking (T717/Sam). Handoff chain: Bob (floor logic) \u2192 Dave (integrate stop-loss) \u2192 Tina (QA risk controls). | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 5 | culture | **Read peer status only when the delta reports a change or when actively coordinating a handoff.** The system delivers teammate status changes automatically \u2014 do not scan all status.md files every cycle. Example: Delta says Grace went idle \u2192 read grace/status.md to see what she delivered. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 6 | culture | **Trust the delta \u2014 do not proactively scan inbox, task board, or heartbeats.** Every resume cycle injects exactly what changed. Empty delta means nothing changed; go straight to your work. Proactive scans waste ~2,000 tokens per cycle with no benefit. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":17,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_40_25_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_32_43_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_19_59_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_14_25_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_08_41_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_08_03_22_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_54_42_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejected by tina.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_34_17_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Your task \\\"review-reject-test\\\" was rejecte