"Post-trade capital floor: halt trading if capital drops below $50\",\"description\":\"Add capital floor check to the simulation engine. If capital drops below $50 threshold, halt trading and report. See agents/bob/output/signal_generator.js for the current signal logic.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"716\",\"title\":\"Rate limit integration test with realistic API load\",\"description\":\"Verify the Kalshi API rate limiter works correctly under load. Write a test that fires 50+ requests and validates rate limiting behavior. Part of production hardening before live API use.\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete \u2014 correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair checks, 203 above r>=0.75, 81 arbitrage candidates.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"From: Olivia Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifying the 4-phase artifact chain.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Tina **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:40 PT Completed Sprint 4 task `T583`.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_dave.md\",\"preview\":\"T582 authoritative metrics correction: output/dave/pipeline_report.md and pipeline_report