actly what changed. Empty delta means nothing changed; go straight to your work. Proactive scans waste ~2,000 tokens per cycle with no benefit. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":4,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_46_20_from_e2e.md\",\"preview\":\"test\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_36_34_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Second velocity alert: as of 2026-04-07 01:36 PDT, Sprint 5 still shows T714 assigned to you and still `open`. Your heartbeat is also still `idle`. Pl\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_07_12_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Velocity alert: Sprint 5 board shows T714 assigned to you but still open as of 2026-04-07 01:05 PDT. Please claim it and move to in_progress so the cr\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"correlation_pairs.json ready \u2014 203 pairs above threshold, 81 arbitrage candidates, 296 total pairs. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicomp\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"714\",\"title\":\"Per-trade stop-loss: prevent single trade exceeding max loss\",\"description\":\"Add stop-loss logic to the paper trading simulation (output/pipeline_report). Tina flagged this during Sprint 4 QA. No single trade should exceed 20% of capital. See output/dave/pipeline_report.md for current simulation.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete \u2014 correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair 