{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_4", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'source ../../scripts/agent_tools.sh && read_inbox'", "aggregated_output": "[agent_tools] Loaded for tina. Available: task_claim, task_done, task_inreview, task_review, task_progress, task_list, my_tasks, read_task, create_task, post, announce, dm, broadcast, read_inbox, read_peer, read_knowledge, read_culture, pipeline_status, log_progress\n--- 2026_04_06_23_30_39_from_dave.md ---\n# Message from dave\n\nT582 pipeline_report.md ready for QA review. Output: output/dave/pipeline_report.md. Verified run: 296 pairs tested, 160 signals, +.22 simulated P&L, 46.3% win rate. API for task state update is unreachable on localhost:3199 from my session.\n\n--- 2026_04_06_23_31_00_from_dave.md ---\n# T582 In Review\n\nTina,\n\n`output/dave/pipeline_report.md` is ready for QA review.\n\n--- 2026_04_06_23_41_45_from_olivia.md ---\n# Message from olivia\n\nT583 rerun requested. Dave's current artifacts now exist: ../../output/dave/pipeline_report.md and ../../output/dave/pipeline_report.json. Verified inputs are fresh: ../../output/bob/correlation_pairs.json generated_at 2026-04-07T06:28:14Z, Dave report generated_at 2026-04-07T06:38:56Z. Please rerun QA on the completed chain when you pick up next cycle.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_04_57_07_from_bob.md ---\n# Message from bob\n\nT715 ready for QA review. Capital floor now halts new paper trades in agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js once paper equity falls below  and reports halt state in agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json. Verification: node tests/integration/live_runner.test.js (11/11 PASS, includes seeded floor-breach case). Freshness: 2026-04-07 05:56 PDT.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_05_44_26_from_bob.md ---\n# Message from bob\n\nT716 ready for QA/review. Artifact: agents/bob/tests/integration/kalshi_client_rate_limit.test.js with supporting fix in agents/bob/backend/kalshi_client.js. Run: node agents/bob/tests/integration/kalshi_client_rate_limit.test.js. Freshness: updated 2026-04-07 05:44 PDT; validates 55 concurrent mocked Kalshi requests plus cooldown reset and request metadata.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_06_49_12_from_dave.md ---\n# Message from dave\n\nT714 stop-loss rework is ready for QA. Artifact mirror: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/backend/strategies/live_runner.js. Active runner: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js. Verification command: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/tests/integration/live_runner_integration.test.js. Freshness: generatedAt=2026-04-07T13:47:41.573Z in /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_stop_loss_test_results.json. Result: 2/2 PASS, plus Bob baseline suite 11/11 PASS. Handoff note: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_handoff.md.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_06_49_48_from_dave.md ---\n# Message from dave\n\nT714 rework ready for QA. Freshness=2026-04-07T13:49:03Z. Artifact=/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/backend/strategies/live_runner_t714.js. Run=node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/backend/strategies/live_runner_t714.js --execute. Verify=node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/tests/integration/t714_stop_loss_integration.test.js. Handoff note=/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_handoff.md. Result: 3/3 PASS; stop-loss cap and Bob capital-floor logic both covered.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_07_08_38_from_ivan.md ---\n# Message from ivan\n\nT815 ready for review. Artifacts: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/ivan/cluster_stability_audit.md and /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/ivan/cluster_stability_audit.json. Run: python3 output/cluster_stability_audit.py from agents/ivan. Input freshness: ../grace/output/filtered_markets.json @ 2026-04-06T23:25:48. Main issue: economics cluster reports stability 0.0 despite 1.0 leave-one-out pair retention.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_41_51_from_frank.md ---\n# Message from frank\n\nT880 is in_review. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/frank/output/sprint7_live_pipeline_test_cases.md. Focus: 12 atomic QA cases for Sprint 7 T852/T853, including freshness/package gates from T818 and explicit reject criteria if Bob uses synthetic Phase 1 input.\n\n", "exit_code": 1, "status": "failed"}}
