{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_34", "type": "agent_message", "text": "Reviewed the active queue.\n\n`T852` is approved. I verified freshness on [live_fixture_e2e_report.json](/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/t852/live_fixture_e2e_report.json), reran `node output/bob/run_live_fixture_pipeline.js` against Grace\u2019s live fixture, and confirmed the pipeline completes end-to-end. Phase 1-3 and the approved signal count reproduced cleanly. The only residual risk is Phase 4 nondeterminism: Bob\u2019s submitted report shows 1 trade / `0.45` PnL, while my rerun produced 2 trades / `0.60` PnL.\n\n`T870` is rejected. Liam\u2019s triage note at [t870_alt002_triage.md](/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/liam/t870_alt002_triage.md) was fresh, but fresh evidence in [health_check_log.jsonl](/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/public/reports/health_check_log.jsonl) showed new `/api/health` spikes after the report timestamp: `2026-04-07T17:19:11.649Z = 575ms` and `2026-04-07T17:21:12.027Z = 950ms`. I DM\u2019d Liam and Alice and posted the blocker to team channel."}}
